# Keep Docker build contexts small. Build context for api/web is the monorepo root.

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/.uv-cache
**/.uv-python
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/venv
**/.venv
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.prod.example
**/.git
**/.github
**/e2e
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/*.md
!packages/shared-types/**
infra/.env.prod
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/agent-transcripts
